    <p>My wife and I had a pleas­ant sur­prise re­cently when we were vis­ited by two vol­un­teers from our hous­ing es­tate’s com­mu­nity cen­tre.</p>
    <p>They gave us a let­ter to claim the Asian Med­i­cal Foun­da­tion Sil­ver Care Fund Vouch­ers worth $100 each.</p>
    <p>We wish to ex­press our grat­i­tude to the foun­da­tion for its mag­na­nim­ity dur­ing this dif­fi­cult pe­riod caused by the Covid-19 pan­demic.</p>


